item.title: protobuf 사용
item.description: 설치 protoc 최신 버전 확인 ( https://github.com/google/protobuf/releases ) $ curl -OL https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protobuf/releases/download/v3.15.6/protoc-3.15.6-linux-x86_64.zip $ unzip protoc-3.6.1-linux-x86\_64.zip -d protoc3 $ sudo mv protoc3/bin/\* /usr/local/bin/ $ sudo mv protoc3/include/\* /usr/local/include/ $ sudo chown $USER /usr/local/bin/protoc $ sudo chown -R $USER /usr/local/include/google 원본: Install protobuf 3.6.1 on Ubuntu 16.04 (github.com) (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
